    notes:
      '* <i>Death Surge</i> will grant the bonus movement speed after a brief delay.\n<ul><li><ul><li>The buff is intended to grant 75% decaying movement speed, but instead grants 67% movement speed decaying with -8% per stat update.\n<ul><li>Precisely this leaves him at <span data-top_values="0;0.26;0.53;0.79;1.06;1.32;1.58;1.85;2.11;2.38;2.64" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" class="pp-tooltip" data-top_label="time passed" data-displayformula="67% after 0 to 0.32 seconds, then &nbsp;−&nbsp;8% per stat update" data-bot_values="0;67;59;51;43;35;27;19;11;3;0" data-bot_key="%">0% − 0% (based on time passed)</span> bonus movement speed.</li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li><i>Death Surge</i> has a shared cooldown across each ability key, regardless of which key is used to activate it. Thus, activating <i>Death Surge</i> with any ability key will put the others on cooldown.</li>\n<li><i>Death Surge\'s</i> cooldown resets upon death.</li>\n<li><i>Death Surge\'s</i> cooldown is affected by <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a title="Ability haste" href="/wiki/Ability_haste"><img width="15" data-image-key="Cooldown_reduction_icon.png" alt="Cooldown reduction icon" decoding="async" data-image-name="Cooldown reduction icon.png" data-relevant="0" class="lazyload" loading="lazy" height="15" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/95/Cooldown_reduction_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203444" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D"></a>&nbsp;ability haste</span> and thus the ability is technically able to be used up to twice during a single instance of <i>Glory in Death</i>, but this isn\'t practical.\n<ul><li><i>Death Surge</i> is not affected by <span style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-game="lol" class="inline-image label-after rune-icon" data-rune="Ultimate Hunter"><span data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;"><a href="/wiki/Ultimate_Hunter_(Rune)" title="Ultimate Hunter"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e4/Ultimate_Hunter_rune.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180509080323" decoding="async" width="20" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" loading="lazy" alt="Ultimate Hunter" data-image-key="Ultimate_Hunter_rune.png" data-relevant="0" height="20" data-image-name="Ultimate Hunter rune.png"></a></span> <span style="word-break: keep-all;;"><a href="/wiki/Ultimate_Hunter_(Rune)" title="Ultimate Hunter (Rune)" class="mw-redirect">Ultimate Hunter</a></span></span>, even if cast from the ultimate ability slot.</li>\n<li>Despite showing the cooldown being reduced, <i>Death Surge</i> in the ultimate ability slot will be not reduced by <span style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" class="inline-image label-after item-icon" data-item="Axiom Arc" data-game="lol"><span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;"><a title="Axiom Arc\'s" href="/wiki/Axiom_Arc"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/03/Axiom_Arc_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20211020233329" width="20" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="Axiom Arc\'s" data-image-name="Axiom Arc item.png" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-key="Axiom_Arc_item.png" data-relevant="0"></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Axiom_Arc" title="Axiom Arc">Axiom Arc\'s</a></span></span> <a title="Named item effect" href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Flux">Flux</a> on <span data-tip="Takedown" class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol"><a title="Takedown" href="/wiki/Takedown"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/07/Damage_rating.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170514053710" loading="lazy" data-image-name="Damage rating.png" height="20" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20" data-image-key="Damage_rating.png" alt="Damage rating" class="lazyload" data-relevant="0" decoding="async"></a> <a title="Takedown" href="/wiki/Takedown">takedown</a></span>.<sup><span style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" class="basic-tooltip" title="This is not intended.">(bug)</span></sup></li>\n<li><i>Death Surge\'s</i> cooldown is not reduced by <span style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-item="Navori Quickblades" data-param="" data-game="lol" class="inline-image label-after item-icon"><span data-width="20" class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;"><a href="/wiki/Navori_Quickblades" title="Navori Quickblades\'"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e6/Navori_Quickblades_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201029200723" data-relevant="0" decoding="async" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" class="thumbborder lazyload" alt="Navori Quickblades\'" width="20" data-image-name="Navori Quickblades item.png" height="20" loading="lazy" data-image-key="Navori_Quickblades_item.png"></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Navori_Quickblades" title="Navori Quickblades">Navori Quickblades\'</a></span></span> <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Deft_Strike" title="Named item effect">Deft Strike</a>.</li></ul></li></ul>',
